summary: THE CONTACT OWNS A 2007 DOREL JUVENILE GROUP ALPHA ELITE BOOSTER SEAT.  HE OBSERVED THAT THE BOOSTER SEAT'S SHARP BASE DAMAGED FOUR AREAS OF THE BACK LEFT REAR OF THE VEHICLE.  MOREOVER, THE REAR BASE SUPPORT CURLED AND FOLDED OVER WHICH CHALLENGED THE STURDINESS OF THE SEAT.  THE CONTACT DISCONTINUED USE OF THE BOOSTER SEAT.
